BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Thedirt": "https://thedirt.online/event/intermediate-watercolor-painting-with-misuk-goltz-6-sessions/2026-04-07/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:thedirt
X-SOURCE:The Dirt
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T120000
DTSTAMP:20260407T102545
CREATED:20260219T060443Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260224T223946Z
UID:10075346-1775556000-1775563200@thedirt.online
SUMMARY:Intermediate Watercolor Painting with Misuk Goltz (6-Sessions)
DESCRIPTION:Intermediate Watercolor Painting with Misuk Goltz\nTuesdays\, 10 AM – 12 PM\nMar. 24\, 31 & Apr. 7\, 14\, 21 & May 5 (no class Apr. 28)\n$195 Members | $215 Non-Members (Materials not included) \nIn this 6-week workshop\, students will create watercolor paintings inspired by Misuk’s recent travels to Italy\, Croatia\, Montenegro\, Greece\, and Turkey. Using these Mediterranean image references\, participants will explore landscape\, architectural\, and figurative subjects rich in light\, atmosphere and color. Students will focus on designing harmonious compositions\, developing value studies for each subject\, and working with limited color palettes to achieve cohesive\, painterly results. For this workshop\, participants should have prior experience with watercolor techniques and color blending. \nRegister here: https://pencegallery.org/education/programs/workshops-and-classes/ \nAny questions? Email pencegallery@gmail.com.
URL:https://thedirt.online/event/intermediate-watercolor-painting-with-misuk-goltz-6-sessions/2026-04-07/
LOCATION:Pence Gallery\, 212 D Street\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thedirt.online/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/IMG_5386.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Pence Gallery":MAILTO:pencegallery@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"UC Davis Library": "https://events.library.ucdavis.edu/event/davis-r-users-group-2026"}
X-SOURCE-ID:ucdavis_library
SUMMARY:Davis R Users' Group
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T120000
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51754758581194
DESCRIPTION:D-RUG\, our local R Users' Group\, meets weekly to facilitate 
 learning and using the R software language. R users from all domains are i
 nvited to bring their R-specific coding problems and share their experienc
 e with other members of the community. Meetup formats include everything f
 rom group discussion and mini-workshops to coworking sessions. D-RUG is ru
 n by volunteer Coo[R]dinators including UC Davis data scientists and gradu
 ate students dedicated to growing and strengthening the R community.\n\n \
 n\nToday's session is open-forum format to foster a communal\, co-working 
 environment. Come hang out and chat\, work on your own\, seek and give hel
 p\, and make friends.\n\n \n\nD-RUG meets Thursdays in person from 10 AM t
 o 12 PM at the DataLab Classroom (Shields Library room 360) on the UC Davi
 s campus. \n\nSign up for our mailing list to get the most up to date info
 rmation\, including a Zoom link to join us virtually if you can't make it 
 in person. Learn more about D-RUG on our website.
LOCATION:Shields Library\, 360
URL:https://events.library.ucdavis.edu/event/davis-r-users-group-2026
X-SOURCE:UC Davis Library
END:VEVENT
