DESCRIPTION:The annual CSSA conference is a place for undergraduate and gr
 aduate students of all majors to learn about cognitive science in both aca
 demia and in industry. The conference and club aim to empower attendees to
  learn about the field and the diverse opportunities it entails\, provide 
 an environment for everyone to broaden their network\, and meet other stud
 ents. \n\nWe hope to provide this throughout the conference through many k
 ey events\, including professional and student networking sessions and int
 eractive speaker and panel events.
