BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Davis Downtown": "https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year-2/2026-05-27/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:davis_downtown
SUMMARY:Picnic in the Park at Davis Farmers Market – Wednesday Evenings 
 (50th Anniversary Year)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T200000
UID:10000519-1779897600-1779912000@davisdowntown.com
DESCRIPTION:The beloved Picnic in the Park season is back at the Davis Far
 mers Market starting Wednesday\, April 1\, 2026! \nEvery Wednesday evening
  through August 26\, the market expands to 4:00 – 8:00 PM\, turning Cent
 ral Park into the perfect spot for a relaxed picnic dinner. Shop fresh pro
 duce\, artisan goods\, and a wide variety of prepared foods from your favo
 rite vendors. Enjoy local craft beer\, wine\, and brand new this year – 
 mead! \nEach week features live music and children’s activities\, creati
 ng a festive\, family-friendly atmosphere. Bring blankets\, lawn chairs\, 
 and reusable bags. It’s the ideal way to unwind\, connect with neighbors
 \, and support local farmers and food makers. \nThis year is extra special
  as the Davis Farmers Market celebrates its 50th Anniversary! Don’t miss
  the big anniversary celebration on Saturday\, August 1\, 2026. \nNew in 2
 026: The Market Memories Cookbook (presale now at davis-farmers-market). \
 nHighlights Include: \n\nBuckhorn Food Truck\, The Hotdogger\, Dhillon Far
 m\, Davis Bread & Desserts\, Greek Table\, Kettle Pop & more\nLive music e
 very week\nKids’ activities\nLocal beer\, wine & mead\n\nFree to attend 
 – everyone is welcome!
LOCATION:Central Park\, 301 C St.\, Davis\, CA\, 95616\, United States
URL:https://davisdowntown.com/event/davis-farmers-market-year-round-fresh-
 local-in-central-park-50th-anniversary-year-2/2026-05-27/
X-SOURCE:Davis Downtown
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup Yolo County Board Game Gathering": "https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/events/rwnqstyjchbkc/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_yolo_county_board_game_gathering
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Yolo Board Game Gathering
UID:event_rwnqstyjchbkc@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T172544Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260527T210000
SUMMARY:Weekly Game Night at Blue Note
DESCRIPTION:Yolo County Board Game Gathering\nUpdate 8/14/25:\n**We're sti
 ll active**\, but we primarily use Discord to chat and plan events. (See g
 roup description for invite link.)\n\nWe still meet every Wednesday for bo
 ard games at Blue Note Brewing Company. We'll have a handful of tables res
 erved near the back\; just look for the pile of board games.\n\nPeople usu
 ally start arriving around 5pm\, and games start whenever people are ready
 . Blue Note closes at 9pm\, and although we have a 5-10 minute grace perio
 d there\, you should be in the process of final scoring by 9\, or else pac
 k it up and play again another day.\n\nGame night is open to all ages! Blu
 e Note is a brewery\, not a bar\, so there's no restriction against minors
 . In addition to their crafted-in-house beer selection\, water and sodas a
 re available.\n\nYou're not required to buy anything in order to join us\,
  but we do encourage you to support local businesses. Blue Note's chef tea
 m makes a mean pizza\, and there are other nearby downtown restaurants and
  businesses.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/yolo-county-board-game-gathering/even
 ts/rwnqstyjchbkc/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20250814T213526Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20250814T213526Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
