 vely energy of downtown Davis. Perfect for unwinding after work\, meeting 
 friends\, or a casual date night. Bring blankets or chairs for relaxed vib
 es. \nSupport local musicians\, eateries\, and businesses while soaking in
  spring’s longer days. No tickets needed – just show up! \nDate/Time: 
 Thursdays at 6:00 PM (April 2\, April 9\, April 23\, April 30\, May 7\, Ma
 y 21\, May 28\, June 4\, June 11\, June 18) \nLocation: G Street platform
